data.description: This Charming home presents the perfect blend of modern updates while providing a peaceful setting for comfort and relaxation.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has undergone numerous updates.  Step inside to discover a warm and inviting space with lots of natural light with a functional layout.  Discover your spacious kitchen featuring with all new hardware on the cabinets and a beautiful backsplash provides both style and creativity for your cooking adventures.  Enjoy new lighting throughout much of this home, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings or quiet evenings at home.  Both full bathrooms have received attention with new hardware, backsplash, shower head and faucets.  A newer roof & skylights were installed in 2023 adds to the peace of mind & insures years of protection against the elements. The full, unfinished basement offers endless potential for additional living space, home gym, workshop, or recreational room for entertaining family and friends.  A newer 10x16 shed provides ample space for storing tools, equipment, and seasonal items, ensuring your home remains clutter-free and organized.  Surround yourself with the beauty of mature landscaping, including lilac bushes, hostas, daffodils and peony's. Each season brings its own delightful display of colors and scents. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own!
